{"tid":479691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"住係地底既火星人日日笑鳩地球人","createTime":"2017-11-25T11:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T13:25:21.000Z","uid":65024,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7303b3fb2c26f86fe952bb9a03b199217185d26f","tid":479691,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"大家諗下，只要有技術，住地底根本一定好過住地面<br />\n將地底挖到一千座ＩＦＣ咁深，制造人工天空話咁易，成個世界已經無晒天氣影響，日日都咁好天，仲有數之不盡既好處<br />\n<br />\n所以如果有外星高等智慧生命，根本好大機會係唔會住係星球表面！<br />\n認同請正評！"},{"pid":"19a0b2b621a7f9d10b79a1cebeb838dfcb47464e","tid":479691,"uid":65024,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"仲有月球，美國佬當年上完去就已經知地底有野，再繼續上月球有估計唔到既事發生，所以先幾十年都唔再上去<br />\n<br />\n否則大家諗下，幾十年前已經上到月球既美國點解會無啦啦叫停？邊個唔知霸到月球根本就玩撚晒！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3633b5073f09430f42ca44d97e886415291d3ca4","tid":479691,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"27cff0705ca091d9148f6d642e5f21b2398500fe","tid":479691,"uid":108937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o3n69P6Xelc/movieposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fo3n69P6Xelc%2Fmovieposter.jpg&h=669000ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c1fdc334aef70d43d9107b07c763eac699e58c4","tid":479691,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>55</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4322e5b237ce80f735ba9cd9b62fb9e54d48e28","tid":479691,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"1e72bea6c375316127cd0073986f8766a087c96d","tid":479691,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c